679
00:58:19,433 --> 00:58:22,403
I don't know,
it goes into some kind of den.

680
00:58:23,270 --> 00:58:24,705
I couldn't pull it out.

681
00:58:25,139 --> 00:58:27,007
- [Solomon] A den?
- [grunts]

682
00:58:27,041 --> 00:58:28,409
Some kind of hole
in the ground.

683
00:58:29,076 --> 00:58:30,811
It don't really matter,
though, I guess.

684
