713
01:01:03,464 --> 01:01:05,099
I can help you with that, too.

714
01:01:05,132 --> 01:01:06,500
You just have
to trust me a little.

715
01:01:07,201 --> 01:01:09,470
Whatever is out there
ain't gon' go away

716
01:01:09,503 --> 01:01:11,238
